{"nodes": [{"id": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "label": "Backtest e Metriche Oneste (Obsidian truth page)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "concept_perspective_neutral_inference", "label": "Perspective-Neutral Inference Rule", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Permanent rule: any inference outside train.py MUST replicate the training preprocessing (train medians, then StandardScaler) and randomize the row perspective (swap w_/l_ pairs, negate diff_/rank_diff/age_diff/height_diff, invert rank_ratio, 1-p for elo probs). Even with correct preprocessing, non-randomized winner-POV rows show +11pt orientation bias (76% vs 65%)."}, {"id": "concept_fake_85_winrate", "label": "Fake 85% Win-Rate Artifact (4 compounding bugs)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The old src/models/backtest.py reported 85% win rate and an exploding bankroll via four compounding bugs: (1) no scaler/train medians \u2014 raw inputs degenerate the model to 95.6% 'p1 wins' predictions; (2) winner-POV rows never randomized \u2014 betting p1 auto-wins by construction; (3) the 0.5/0.5 implied-prob sentinel passed dropna, creating phantom 2.00 odds; (4) de-vigged fair odds used instead of real B365 prices with margin."}, {"id": "concept_honest_baseline", "label": "Honest Baseline: 66.3% acc / LL 0.608 vs B365 favourite 67.7%", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Leak-free 2025+ test baseline (train 2005-2023, val 2024): ensemble 66.3% acc / LL 0.608 / ROC 0.731; LightGBM single best 67.0%. The B365 favourite scores 67.7% \u2014 the market is still more accurate than the model, hence no predictive edge; honest Quarter-Kelly backtest shows ROI -82%, win rate 43%. This is the baseline every experiment must beat."}], "edges": [{"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "concept_fake_85_winrate", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "concept_honest_baseline", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "concept_perspective_neutral_inference", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": "regola permanente", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "log_metrics_history_script", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "concept_has_odds_flag", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": "bug 3", "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "obsidian_backtest_metriche", "target": "obsidian_feature_engineering", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/obsidian/Backtest_e_Metriche_Oneste.md", "source_location": "[[Feature_Engineering]]", "weight": 